com.pom.crimson.pages

Class ExplorePage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pom.crimson.base.BaseFixture
      • com.pom.crimson.base.BasePage
        • com.pom.crimson.pages.ExplorePage

  • public class ExplorePage
extends BasePage
    Explore Page or Content page displays articles and videos as per user's interests and joined groups.
    User can navigate to this page by :

    Go to Home Page
    Click Content in bottom menu.

    This page class contains MobileElements on this page and functions to simulate interactions with these elements.
    Author:
    Jaspreet Kaur Chagger
